section.section:
Before recording an instrument among the land or financing records, a clerk shall collect:
$10 for a release 9 pages or less in length;
$20 for any other instrument 9 pages or less in length;
Except as provided in item (i) of this paragraph, $20 for an instrument, regardless of length, involving solely a principal residence; and
$75 for any other instrument 10 pages or more in length.
